cd CKDLINUX
  git clone --recursive git@github.com:AER-RC/MT_CKD.git

or

  the source code is at https://github.com/AER-RC/MT_CKD/releases/tag/4.3
  download to home computer then scp it here
  scp MT_CKD-4.3.tar.gz sergio@chip.rs.umbc.edu:///home/sergio/SPECTRA/CKDLINUX/.
    
  tar -xvf MT_CKD-4.3.tar.gz
  this creates  MT_CKD_4.3
  
  cd MT_CKD-4.3
  
  [sergio@c24-52 MT_CKD-4.3]$ ls
  aer_rt_utils  build  data  docs  LBLRTM  README.md  run_example  src

If you do
  ls src
there are lots of dead symbolic links to ../aer_rt_utils/
"aer_rt_utils" is BLANK. So
  cp -a /home/sergio/git/IR_NIR_VIS_UV_RTcodes/LBLRTM/LBLRTM12.17/LBLRTM/aer_rt_utils/* aer_rt_utils

Similarly
  ls src
has lots of dead symbolic links to codes in ../LBLRTM
"LBLRTM" is BLANK
lrwxrwxrwx 1 sergio pi_sergio    24 Apr 17  2024 contnm.f90 -> ../LBLRTM/src/contnm.f90
lrwxrwxrwx 1 sergio pi_sergio    27 Apr 17  2024 lblparams.f90 -> ../LBLRTM/src/lblparams.f90
lrwxrwxrwx 1 sergio pi_sergio    35 Apr 17  2024 mt_ckd_h2o_module.f90 -> ../LBLRTM/src/mt_ckd_h2o_module.f90
lrwxrwxrwx 1 sergio pi_sergio    29 Apr 17  2024 phys_consts.f90 -> ../LBLRTM/src/phys_consts.f90
lrwxrwxrwx 1 sergio pi_sergio    30 Apr 17  2024 planet_earth.f90 -> ../LBLRTM/src/planet_earth.f90
