4) Small modification so you can use your own input file
---------------------------------------------------------

Instead
  cd src
  cp cntnm_progr.f90 cntnm_progr_sergio.f90

edit cntnm_progr_sergio.f90 so you can input O2/N2; set CO2,ARGON to 0.0
edit cntnm_progr_sergio.f90 to comment out calls to PRCNTM
edit cntnm_progr_sergio.f90 to add in HMOLID(22) = '   N2  '
edit cntnm_progr_sergio.f90 to have 0:0.01:3000 calcs instead of 0:10:19900
edit contnm.f90             so turn off rayleigh scattering
           absrb(i) = absrb(i)+ray_ext*0.0  !!! sergio turns off rayleigh

you can do   diff contnm.f90 /home/sergio/git/IR_NIR_VIS_UV_RTcodes/LBLRTM/LBLRTM12.17/LBLRTM/src/.
             diff cntnm_progr_sergio.f90 cntnm_progr.f90

then
  cd build
  cp make_cntnm make_cntnm_sergio
edit it so you call cntnm_progr_sergio.f90
  gmake -f make_cntnm_sergio linuxGNUdbl
and check it has same warnings as   gmake -f make_cntnm linuxGNUdbl
../cntnm_sergio_v4.3_linux_gnu_dbl created

test it with
cd ../run_example
  ../cntnm_v4.3_linux_gnu_dbl
  Push 0, then enter
  ../cntnm_sergio_v4.3_linux_gnu_dbl
  Push 0, then enter

Now make generic test inputs, DO NOT CHANGE THEM
   n2_input : every gas 0 except N2
   o2_input : every gas 0 except 02   
   wv_input : WV VMR = 0.1, and has N2 = 0.78*WTOT, O2 = 0.21*WTOT
   
 ../cntnm_sergio_v4.3_linux_gnu_dbl < wv_input; /bin/mv CNTNM.OPTDPT wv.OPTDPT
 ../cntnm_sergio_v4.3_linux_gnu_dbl < o2_input; /bin/mv CNTNM.OPTDPT o2.OPTDPT
 ../cntnm_sergio_v4.3_linux_gnu_dbl < n2_input; /bin/mv CNTNM.OPTDPT n2.OPTDPT
clc; head o2.OPTDPT; head n2.OPTDPT; head wv.OPTDPT;

check  
  addpath ~/SPECTRA/CKDLINUX/
  wv = read_MT_CKD4p3_sergio('/home/sergio/SPECTRA/CKDLINUX/MT_CKD-4.3/run_example/wv.OPTDPT');
  o2 = read_MT_CKD4p3_sergio('/home/sergio/SPECTRA/CKDLINUX/MT_CKD-4.3/run_example/o2.OPTDPT');
  n2 = read_MT_CKD4p3_sergio('/home/sergio/SPECTRA/CKDLINUX/MT_CKD-4.3/run_example/n2.OPTDPT');
  semilogy(o2.data(:,1),o2.data(:,2),n2.data(:,1),n2.data(:,2),'g.-',wv.data(:,1),wv.data(:,2),'rx');
    xlim([605 2830]); legend('o2','n2','wv','location','best')

junk  = find(n2.data(:,2) > 0 & n2.data(:,1) > 0600 & n2.data(:,1) < 3000);
  n2range(1) = min(n2.data(junk,1)); n2range(2) = max(n2.data(junk,1));
junk  = find(o2.data(:,2) > 0 & o2.data(:,1) > 0600 & o2.data(:,1) < 3000);
  o2range(1) = min(o2.data(junk,1)); o2range(2) = max(o2.data(junk,1)); 

